
    <div class = "floating-alert" id="floating-alert">
        <div class="alert-info">
            <div class="class-modal" >
                {# 警醒設定畫面 #}
                <form id="close-modal__form" class="flex flex-column gap-4">
                    <h1 class="class-modal__title">警醒資訊</h1>
                    <fieldset>
                        <legend>警醒</legend>
                        <div class="field"  id="alertType">
                            <label for="alert-interval">警醒類型:</label>
                            <label id="alert-type" class="alert-type"></label>
                        </div>
                        <label for="alert-interval">警醒間隔:</label>
                        <div class="field">
                            <input id="alert-interval" class="alert-interval" name="alert-interval" type="number" readonly='readonly' min="10" max="50" required>
                            <label for="alert-interval">分鐘</label>
                        </div>
                        <label for="alert-time">警醒持續時間:</label>
                        <div class="field">
                            <input id="alert-time" class="alert-time" name="alert-time" type="number" readonly='readonly' min="1" max="3" required>
                            <label for="alert-time">分鐘</label>
                        </div>
                    </fieldset>
                    <div class="type-info">
                        <fieldset class="fieldset">

                        </fieldset>
                    </div>

                    <div class="error-text"></div>

                    <div class="center-btn">
                        <button type="button" id="setting" class="margin-inline-start-auto btn-primary">修改</button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="center-btn" hidden>
                        <input type="submit" id="submit-form" hidden disabled/>
                        <button type="button" id="submit-setting" class="margin-inline-start-auto btn-primary">確定</button>
                        <button type="button" id="cancel-setting" class="margin-inline-start-auto btn-primary">取消</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="alert_icon_buttons" id="alert-exchange">
                <i class='bx bx-repost'></i>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-choose close">
            <div class="alert_icon_buttons" id="alert-return">
                <i class='bx bx-arrow-back'></i>
            </div>
            <div class="class-modal">
                <h1 class="class-modal__title">選擇你想要的警醒類型</h1>
                <div class="page-content">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                        <h2 class="title">警醒按鈕</h2>
                        <p class="copy">會議主辦人可設定警醒按鈕顯示之間隔以及按鈕顯示持續時間，當時間到時並顯示警醒按鈕在參加會議者畫面任意處供點擊簽到。</p>
                        <button class="btn" id="choose-1">選擇</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                        <h2 class="title">選擇題警醒</h2>
                        <p class="copy">搭配警醒按鈕，附加選擇題，從一組選項當中，選出一個作為正確的答案，並完成警醒簽到。</p>
                        <button class="btn" id="choose-2">選擇</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                        <h2 class="title">問答題警醒</h2>
                        <p class="copy">搭配警醒按鈕，附加問答題，讓會議者簡述回答問題，並完成警醒簽到。</p>
                        <button class="btn" id="choose-3">選擇</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                        <h2 class="title">投票式警醒</h2>
                        <p class="copy">搭配警醒按鈕，附加投票，典型的手法讓群體經過討論或辯論後，在特定紙張上標示出投票者的立場，並完成警醒簽到。</p>
                        <button class="btn" id="choose-4">選擇</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert-step-progress button-setting close">
            <div class="alert_icon_buttons" id="alert-btn-return" style="left: 15px;">
                <i class="bx bx-arrow-back"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="class-modal__title">警醒按鈕設定</h1>
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>警醒</legend>
                    <div class="error-text"></div>
                    <label for="alert-interval">警醒間隔:</label>
                    <div class="field">
                        <input id="alert-interval" class="alert-interval" name="alert-interval" type="number" required="" min="10" max="50">
                        <label for="alert-interval">分鐘</label>
                    </div>
                    <label for="alert-time">警醒持續時間:</label>
                    <div class="field">
                        <input id="alert-time" class="alert-time" name="alert-time" type="number" required="" min="1" max="3">
                        <label for="alert-time">分鐘</label>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
                <div class="center-btn">
                    <button type="button" id="alert-btn-finish" class="margin-inline-start-auto btn-primary">設定完成</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert-step-progress multiple-choice-setting close">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="class-modal__title">設定選擇題流程</h1>
                <div class="process-bar">
                    <div class="step">
                        <p>問題</p>
                        <div class="bullet">
                            <span>1</span>
                        </div>
                        <i class='bx bx-check check'></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <p>選項</p>
                        <div class="bullet">
                            <span>2</span>
                        </div>
                        <i class='bx bx-check check'></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <p>警醒</p>
                        <div class="bullet">
                            <span>3</span>
                        </div>
                        <i class='bx bx-check check'></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-outer">
                    <div class="form-inner">
                        <div class="page slidepage">
                            <div class="title">輸入題目問題</div>
                            <div class="field">
                                <div class="label">Question:</div>
                                <div class="error-text" ></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field">
                                <textarea class="qst_text" cols="45" rows="10" maxlength="50"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field btns">
                                <button class="prev-1 prev">返回</button>
                                <button class="next-1 next">下一步</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="page page-2">
                            <div class="title">輸入選項</div>
                            
                            <div class="field">
                                <div class="error-text"></div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="options">
                                <div class="field add">
                                    <button class="add_options">新增選項</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="field btns">
                                <button class="prev-2 prev">上一步</button>
                                <button class="next-2 next">下一步</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="page">
                            <div class="title">警醒設定</div>
                            <div class="field">
                                <div class="error-text"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field alert">
                                <label for="alert-interval">警醒間隔:</label>
                                <div class="field">
                                    <input id="alert-interval" class="alert-interval" name="alert-interval" type="number" min="10" max="50">
                                    <label for="alert-interval">分鐘</label>
                                </div>
                                <label for="alert-time">警醒持續時間:</label>
                                <div class="field">
                                    <input id="alert-time" class="alert-time" name="alert-time" type="number" min="1" max="3">
                                    <label for="alert-time">分鐘</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="field btns">
                                <button class="prev-3 prev">上一步</button>
                                <button class="next-3 next">完成</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert-step-progress essay-question close">

            <div class="alert_icon_buttons" id="alert-essay-question-return">
                <i class="bx bx-arrow-back"></i>
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="class-modal__title">設定問答題</h1>

                <div class="error-text"></div>

                <fieldset>
                    <legend>問答題</legend>
                    <label for="alert-interval">Question:</label>

                    <div class="field">
                        <textarea class="qst_text" cols="25" rows="5" maxlength="50"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>

                <fieldset>
                    <legend>警醒</legend>
                    <label for="alert-interval">警醒間隔:</label>
                    <div class="field">
                        <input id="essay-question__alert-interval" class="alert-interval" name="alert-interval" type="number" required="" min="10" max="50">
                        <label for="alert-interval">分鐘</label>
                    </div>
                    <label for="alert-time">警醒持續時間:</label>
                    <div class="field">
                        <input id="essay-question__alert-time" class="alert-time" name="alert-time" type="number" required="" min="1" max="3">
                        <label for="alert-time">分鐘</label>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
                <div class="center-btn">
                    <button type="button" id="essay-question-finish" class="margin-inline-start-auto btn-primary">設定完成</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>